    examTip: "Remember that the failure-to-file penalty is ten times higher than the failure-to-pay penalty; always prioritize filing on time, even if you need to request an extension or arrange a payment plan.",
    memoryAid: "File First, Pay Later (FFPL) - Prioritize filing to avoid the higher penalty.",
    reference: "IRC §6651",
