    options: ["Any property distribution results in a loss","The distribution consists SOLELY of cash, unrealized receivables, and inventory, AND the partner's outside basis exceeds the partnership's basis in the distributed property (including cash)","The partner receives less cash than contributed","The partnership has overall losses"],
