    examTip: "Focus on the 'qualified lender' and 'secured by real property' aspects of qualified nonrecourse financing to quickly eliminate incorrect answer choices on the exam.",
    memoryAid: "Think 'QRR': Qualified lender, Real property, Recourse (no personal recourse).",
    reference: "IRC §465(b)(6)",
