      1: "Why option B is WRONG - Delivery of collateral by itself is insufficient for attachment. While possession can substitute for a written security agreement, value and debtor rights are still required.",
      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Filing a financing statement is a step towards perfection, not attachment. Attachment must occur before perfection can be effective.",
