    examTip: "When answering OIC questions, remember the three main reasons the IRS will accept: doubt as to liability, doubt as to collectibility, and effective tax administration.",
    memoryAid: "Think of 'DICE' - Doubt (liability), Inability to pay (collectibility), Circumstances (effective tax administration), Equity.",
