    examTip: "Focus on the 'didn't know and no reason to know' element when evaluating innocent spouse questions; this is often the key differentiator in the fact pattern.",
    memoryAid: "INK: Innocent, No Knowledge, Inequitable = Innocent Spouse Relief",
