    options: ["The contract is enforceable only to the extent of the goods received and accepted or paid for","The entire contract is enforceable because partial performance removes it from the Statute of Frauds","The contract is completely unenforceable because the total exceeds $500","The contract is enforceable for $4,000 only — the amount paid"],
