    examTip: "Focus on whether the grantor survives the QPRT term when determining estate tax consequences; survival means exclusion, death during the term means inclusion.",
    memoryAid: "QPRT: Quit Property, Retain Term. Survive the Term, Estate is Firm (asset excluded).",
