    options: ["A penalty of $0, because the position was disclosed and the taxpayer is responsible for the accuracy of the return.","A penalty of $1,000, due to the unreasonable position.","A penalty equal to the greater of $1,000 or 50% of the income Jane derived (or to be derived) from the return.","A penalty equal to the understatement of $6,000."],
    correctAnswer: 2,
