    question: "Lisa is a 30% partner in the KLM Partnership. During the current year, KLM's ordinary business income was $200,000 before considering any guaranteed payments to partners. Lisa received a guaranteed payment of $60,000 for services rendered to the partnership. What amount should Lisa report as net earnings from self-employment as a result of her relationship with KLM?",
