      2: "Alice recognizes a loss, not a gain.",
      3: "This answer incorrectly calculates the loss by only considering cash and fair market value of the assets instead of the cash and the partnership's basis in the inventory and land. In a liquidating distribution, the partner takes a substituted basis in the distributed assets.",
